sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>incident</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="incident">sys_mod_countVALCHANGES^assignment_group=5ab2b30adb020300dbccf7fdbf96199e^EQ<item endquery="false" field="sys_mod_count" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="VALCHANGES" or="false" value=""/><item display_table="sys_user_group" display_value="Application Provider" endquery="false" field="assignment_group" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="5ab2b30adb020300dbccf7fdbf96199e"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>SIAM_Incident_AG_Patch</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
//gs.log('Running Rest due to update in Red instance');
	
var wrk = current.work_notes.getJournalEntry(1).toString();
var sub= wrk.indexOf(' (Work notes)');
//gs.log(sub);
//gs.log(wrk.length);
var wrk_notes = wrk.substring(sub+13,wrk.length).trim();
gs.log('****'+wrk_notes+'****');

if(!current.u_sys_id_green.nil())	
	{
try { 
 var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident', 'Patch_Incident');
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact1', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes1', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cst_num', current.number);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assign_group1', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state1', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to1', current.assigned_to);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller1', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description1', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service1', current.business_service.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci1', current.cmdb_ci);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency1', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type1', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category1', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('priority1', current.priority);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('sys_id2', current.u_sys_id_green);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory1', current.subcategory);

//override authentication profile 
//authentication type ='basic'/ 'oauth2'
//r.setAuthentication(authentication type, profile name);

 var response = r.execute();
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
//	gs.addInfoMessage('httpStatus' + httpStatus);
gs.log('httpStatus' + httpStatus);
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
	//gs.addInfoMessage('message' + message);
gs.log('message' + message);
}
} else 

{
	 try { 

var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident', 'POST-Incident');
	 

	 
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact1', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type1', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to1', current.assigned_to.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory1', current.subcategory);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assign_group1', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci1', current.cmdb_ci);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category1', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description1', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency1', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('priority1', current.priority);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state1', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service1', current.business_service);
	
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes1', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller1', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_customer_sys_id', current.sys_id);

 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cst_num', current.number);	 
	 

	 
	 
//	 
 var response = r.execute();
// var queryString = response.;
//	  r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_sys_id_green',queryString);	 
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
 var jsonObject = JSON.parse(responseBody);
//gs.log('Green Sys Id' + jsonObject.result.sys_id);
current.u_sys_id_green = jsonObject.result.sys_id; 
	 current.update();
//	 gs.log('REST data parsed: ' + jsonObject.number );
	 
	// gs.log('This is log'+ responseBody);
	 
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
	//gs.log('Message from green instance '+message);
}
	
}

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>incident</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="incident">cmdb_ci=d0fdbc8437201000deeabfc8bcbe5d33^EQ<item display_table="cmdb_ci" display_value="*DAVID-IBM" endquery="false" field="cmdb_ci" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="d0fdbc8437201000deeabfc8bcbe5d33"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>CI - Application Provider routing- Patch</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
var wrk = current.work_notes.getJournalEntry(1).toString();
var sub= wrk.indexOf(' (Work notes)');
//gs.log(sub);
//gs.log(wrk.length);
var wrk_notes = wrk.substring(sub+13,wrk.length).trim();
gs.log('****'+wrk_notes+'****');
try { 
 var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident', 'Patch_Incident');
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact1', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes1', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cst_num', current.number);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assign_group1', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state1', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to1', current.assigned_to);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller1', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description1', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service1', current.business_service.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci1', current.cmdb_ci);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency1', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type1', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category1', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('priority1', current.priority);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('sys_id2', current.u_sys_id_green);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory1', current.subcategory);

//override authentication profile 
//authentication type ='basic'/ 'oauth2'
//r.setAuthentication(authentication type, profile name);

 var response = r.execute();
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-05 09:45:21</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>8254be90db2f4300dbccf7fdbf961958</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CI - Application Provider routing- Patch</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_8254be90db2f4300dbccf7fdbf961958</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-05 10:27:29</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=8254be90db2f4300dbccf7fdbf961958"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>incident</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="incident">assignment_groupCHANGESTO13a2770adb020300dbccf7fdbf96196a^EQ<item display_table="sys_user_group" display_value="Infrastructure Provider" endquery="false" field="assignment_group" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="CHANGESTO" or="false" value="13a2770adb020300dbccf7fdbf96196a"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>SIAM_Incident_Infra_Post</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

	//	var work_notes2 = "Test";
var wrk = current.work_notes.getJournalEntry(1).toString();
var sub= wrk.indexOf(' (Work notes)');
//gs.log(sub);
//gs.log(wrk.length);
var wrk_notes = wrk.substring(sub+13,wrk.length).trim();
//gs.log('****'+wrk_notes+'****'); 	
	
 try { 
 var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident_Instance3', 'POST-Incident3');
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact3', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency3', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category1', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to1', current.assigned_to.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_customer_sys_id', current.sys_id.toString());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description2', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes1', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service1', current.business_service.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_cust_num',current.number);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller3', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state3', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type1', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory1', current.subcategory);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assg_grp3', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci1',current.cmdb_ci.getDisplayValue());

//r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_cst_num', current.number);	 
//override authentication profile 
//authentication type ='basic'/ 'oauth2'
//r.setAuthentication(authentication type, profile name);

 var response = r.execute();
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
	 
 var jsonObject = JSON.parse(responseBody);
//gs.log('Green Sys Id' + jsonObject.result.sys_id);
current.u_sys_id_red = jsonObject.result.sys_id; 
	 current.update();
	 
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-12-20 11:36:27</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>b45570dbdb4b0300dbccf7fdbf96199b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>5</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SIAM_Incident_Infra_Post</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_b45570dbdb4b0300dbccf7fdbf96199b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-03 11:08:53</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=b45570dbdb4b0300dbccf7fdbf96199b"/></record_update>

var sub= wrk.indexOf(' (Work notes)');
//gs.log(sub);
//gs.log(wrk.length);
var wrk_notes = wrk.substring(sub+13,wrk.length).trim();
gs.log('****'+wrk_notes+'****'); 	

 try { 

var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident', 'POST-Incident');
	 

	 
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact1', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type1', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to1', current.assigned_to.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory1', current.subcategory);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assign_group1', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci1', current.cmdb_ci);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category1', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description1', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency1', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('priority1', current.priority);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state1', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service1', current.business_service);
	
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes1', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller1', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_customer_sys_id', current.sys_id);

 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cst_num', current.number);	 
	 

	 
	 
//	 
 var response = r.execute();
// var queryString = response.;
//	  r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_sys_id_green',queryString);	 
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
 var jsonObject = JSON.parse(responseBody);
//gs.log('Green Sys Id' + jsonObject.result.sys_id);
current.u_sys_id_green = jsonObject.result.sys_id; 
	 current.update();
//	 gs.log('REST data parsed: ' + jsonObject.number );
	 
	// gs.log('This is log'+ responseBody);
	 
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
	//gs.log('Message from green instance '+message);
}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2017-11-26 09:13:45</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>5abde4afdb220300dbccf7fdbf961964</sys_id><sys_mod_count>38</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SIAM_Incident_AG_Post</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_5abde4afdb220300dbccf7fdbf961964</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-12-20 11:45:04</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=5abde4afdb220300dbccf7fdbf961964"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>incident</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="incident">sys_mod_countVALCHANGES^assignment_group=13a2770adb020300dbccf7fdbf96196a^EQ<item endquery="false" field="sys_mod_count" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="VALCHANGES" or="false" value=""/><item display_table="sys_user_group" display_value="Infrastructure Provider" endquery="false" field="assignment_group" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value="13a2770adb020300dbccf7fdbf96196a"/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>SIAM_Incident_Infra_Patch</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {

var wrk = current.work_notes.getJournalEntry(1).toString();
var sub= wrk.indexOf(' (Work notes)');
//gs.log(sub);
//gs.log(wrk.length);
var wrk_notes = wrk.substring(sub+13,wrk.length).trim();
gs.log('****'+wrk_notes+'****');
if(!current.u_sys_id_red.nil())	
	{
	try { 
 var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident_Instance3', 'Patch-Incident-3');
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller3', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state3', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category3', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description3', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory3', current.subcategory);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci3', current.cmdb_ci);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency3', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cst_num', current.number);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact3', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('sys_id3', current.u_sys_id_red);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes3', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('priority3', current.priority);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service3', current.business_service.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type3', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assign_group3', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to3', current.assigned_to);

//override authentication profile 
//authentication type ='basic'/ 'oauth2'
//r.setAuthentication(authentication type, profile name);

 var response = r.execute();
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
}
}else {
	
	 try { 
 var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('SIAM-Incident_Instance3', 'POST-Incident3');
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('impact3', current.impact);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('urgency3', current.urgency);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('category1', current.category);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assigned_to1', current.assigned_to.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_customer_sys_id', current.sys_id.toString());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('short_description2', current.short_description);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('work_notes1', wrk_notes);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('business_service1', current.business_service.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_cust_num',current.number);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('caller3', current.caller_id.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('state3', current.state);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('contact_type1', current.contact_type);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('subcategory1', current.subcategory);
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('assg_grp3', current.assignment_group.getDisplayValue());
 r.setStringParameterNoEscape('cmdb_ci1',current.cmdb_ci.getDisplayValue());

//r.setStringParameterNoEscape('u_cst_num', current.number);	 
//override authentication profile 
//authentication type ='basic'/ 'oauth2'
//r.setAuthentication(authentication type, profile name);

 var response = r.execute();
 var responseBody = response.getBody();
	 
 var jsonObject = JSON.parse(responseBody);
//gs.log('Green Sys Id' + jsonObject.result.sys_id);
current.u_sys_id_red = jsonObject.result.sys_id; 
	 current.update();
	 
 var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
}
catch(ex) {
 var message = ex.getMessage();
}
}
	
	
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-04 09:08:17</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>abb26904dba34300dbccf7fdbf96193a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>SIAM_Incident_Infra_Patch</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_abb26904dba34300dbccf7fdbf96193a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-10 09:59:34</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=abb26904dba34300dbccf7fdbf96193a"/></record_update>
